message.content: <OUTPUT_TEXT>To file pleadings with the court clerk, please ensure that all documents are properly formatted according to the court's requirements, including being signed and dated as necessary. Gather all required documents and make the necessary copies. Submit the original documents along with the required number of copies to the court clerk's office either in person or via mail, depending on the court's submission guidelines. Ensure to receive a stamped copy of the pleadings from the clerk as proof of filing.</OUTPUT_TEXT>
